profile.bio: 20yr old coder. Entirely self-taught. My favorite language is C. I know about ten others. I run some chaotic LFS-like Linux distro. I know some Japanese and I love anime. Favorite games: Skyrim, Touhou, Mother 3. My country's Gov't is broken badly.
